long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you like dogs? Do dog photos cheer you up? Wish you could get one on command?

When then this app is for you!

Select which breed of dog you'd like to see, and this extension will supply a photo of that kind of breed whenever you'd like!
